Method Detail

doJob

public void doJob()
           throws java.lang.Exception
Job main routine : - get the feed URL from configuration ; - loads the URL content and builds the XML feed ; - for each <item> in this feed, creates a new SyndEntry object ; - extracts data from the SyndEntry object and check if there is a matching Article in the database ; - if there's already a matching (URL or title for Tumblr) Article in the database, skip to next feed entry ; - if there's no matching Article, create a new one, mobilize it, and save it in the database.
